comment: /**  * Returns the specialized manager instance that provides tight integration between Camel testing  * features and Spring.  *  * @return a new instance of {@link CamelTestContextManager}.  */
code: /**  * Returns the specialized manager instance that provides tight integration between Camel testing  * features and Spring.  *  * @return a new instance of {@link CamelTestContextManager}.  */ @Override protected TestContextManager createTestContextManager(Class<?> clazz) {     return new CamelTestContextManager(clazz). }

private boolean alreadyRegistered() {     List<TestExecutionListener> list = getTestExecutionListeners().     if (list != null) {         for (TestExecutionListener listener : list) {             if (listener instanceof CamelSpringTestContextLoaderTestExecutionListener) {                 return true.             }         }     }     return false. }
